title: BlueRigger High Speed Mini HDMI to HDMI cable with Ethernet (10 Feet)
description: BlueRigger(TM) High Speed Mini HDMI to HDMI cable HDMI Cables are premium quality cables that allow you to connect your Mini-HDMI-compatible Camcorders, Cameras, Gaming Consoles (not Micro HDMI) to your HDTV or any display device that is HDMI equipped.Mini HDMI to HDMI cable and its uses:Mini HDMI to HDMI cable delivers both high-definition video and digital audio from portable digital devices to your home theater. It offers an ideal way to connect digital devices with mini HDMI (HDMI C) ports to HDTVs or Projectors with full-size HDMI (HDMI A) ports.Quality Picture and Sound- Supports 3D, Ethernet- Guaranteed 1440p, 1080p, 1080i, 720p, 480p, and 480i Resolutions- HDCP Compliant-Full metal jacket connector provides strength, durability and prevents interference as compared to other cables.- Supports True HD Dolby 7.1 and DTS-HD Master Audio-Gold-Plated Connectors:The Mini HDMI to HDMI cable features gold-plated connectors that resist corrosion for signal purity-Compatibility:Camcorders, Cameras, Game Consoles & other Digital Devices with a Mini HDMI portNote: Mini HDMI cable is not compatible with Kindle Fire HD. Please purchase ourMicro HDMI cablefor Kindle Fire HD.Technical Specifications:- Connector Type: Mini HDMI Male (HDMI C), HDMI Male (HDMI A)- Gauge: 30 AWG- Category 2 CertifiedWarrantyThe Mini HDMI to HDMI cable is backed by Limited lifetime warranty.
